Details: All exercises to be done with formaster and stabilisers
Strap length tip of fingers at full draw.
Draw elbow behind, front arm extended
Push draw arm froward as far as possible, maintain posture
2x5s. Slide back end 1cm behind and 1cm in front of anchor
2x5s. Push front arm forward in steady movement for 5s
Hold as long as you can while maintaining posture
